  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="3962147">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3962147/" class="title-link">很难</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3962147"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/46629762/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u46629762-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/46629762/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">某智慧</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-10-14"
      class="main-meta">2010-10-14 21:53:24</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3962147_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  今天在学校图书馆，学法学蛮累时，拿起这本书，想要真正深入而不是泛泛的读它，对于我，一个学文科兼法学的人来说，也是蛮难阅读的，读了一个小时，只读过了8页。 书很旧很旧，已经全部泛黄，可是一旦下了决心，就一定要完成它！当我拿起它时，就是对它的承诺——加油了，晓暮。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/3962147/#comments">(3回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_3962147_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_3962147_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










